# Repo cache: {{owner}}/{{repo}}

## Purpose
Read-only shallow clone of `{{default_branch}}` for [[dev-pr-review]] to consult when reviewing PRs against this repo. Never written to; refreshed via `git fetch + reset --hard` by [[dev-cache-pr-review-repo]].

The Stage 1 heuristic fields above (`build_system`, `type_system`, `test_pattern`, `languages`, etc.) are refreshed on every pull. For Stage 2 prose knowledge (overview, conventions, deps detail), see the companion [[{{knowledge_id}}]] entry.

